\newlabel{fig:larval_impact}{{4}{5}{Impact of larval retention on model performance. Left panel shows RMSE across different larval retention configurations. Right panel shows regional recovery patterns, demonstrating how larval retention affects spatial distribution of recovery}{figure.caption.5}{}}
